org.bubblecloud.zigbee.network.packet.zdo

Class ZDO_MGMT_NWK_UPDATE_REQ

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bubblecloud.zigbee.network.packet.ZToolPacket
      • org.bubblecloud.zigbee.network.packet.zdo.ZDO_MGMT_NWK_UPDATE_REQ

  • public class ZDO_MGMT_NWK_UPDATE_REQ
extends ZToolPacket
    This command is provided to allow updating of network configuration parameters or to request information from devices on network conditions in the local operating environment. Upon receipt, the remote device shall determine from the contents of the ScanDuration parameter whether this request is an update to the ChannelMask and NwkManagerAddr parameters, a channel change command, or a request to scan channels and report the results.
    Author:
    Tommi S.E. Laukkanen
